{"word":"ὑπόμνυμι","slug":"ὑπόμνυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n108818\" key=\"u(po/mnumi\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὑπ-όμνῡμι</orth>, <sense id=\"n108818.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">interpose by oath,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φῂς ὑπομνύς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg008.perseus-grc1:339\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">339</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> codd. (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπομνύς</foreign> Pearson). </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n108818.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram></gramGrp>, in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> law, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">make oath</tr_> (for oneself or another) that something serious prevents a person's appearing in court at the due time, and so <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">apply for a postponement of the trial,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg047.perseus-grc1:39\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">47.39</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὑ. τινὰ δημοσίᾳ ἀπεῖναι στρατευόμενον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg048.perseus-grc1:25\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">48.25</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸν Δημοσθένην τις ὑπωμόσατο ὡς νοσοῦντα</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">applied for an extension of the term</tr_> for Demosthenes on the plea of sickness, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg058.perseus-grc1:43\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">58.43</biblScope> </bibl>: hence, comically, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὑπώμνυτο ὁ μὲν οἶνος ὄξος αὑτὸν εἶναι γνήσιον, τὸ δ᾽ ὄξος οἶνον αὑτὸ μᾶλλον θατέρου</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0458.tlg001:65\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eub.\">Eub.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">65</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>:—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπομοθέντος τούτου</foreign> this <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">affidavit being put in by way of excuse,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg048.perseus-grc1:25\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">48.25</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὑπομοθείσης ταύτης τῆς γραφῆς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0030.tlg007:202\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hyp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">202</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n108818.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in the Assembly or Boule, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">make an objection on oath,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:7:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HG\">HG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.7.34</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.848d</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:8:44\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.44</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}